          + Electronics
               o About
               o Team
               o Contacts

   SUBATECH is a research laboratory co-operated by the Ecole des Mines de
   Nantes, the Institut National de Physique Nucléaire et de Physique des
   Particules (IN2P3) of CNRS, and the Université de Nantes.

   The core research activities at SUBATECH revolve around nuclear physics
   and nuclear chemistry, in their fundamental and applied aspects, as
   well as their experimental and theoretical incarnations.
